%% Diagram: Device token lifecycle
%% Type: state
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Active: App install / token register
    Active --> Active: App launch refresh\n(< 7 days old)
    Active --> Active: Token refresh callback
    Active --> Stale: 30 days inactive
    Stale --> Active: User opens app\n(token re-validated)
    Active --> Invalid: 404 UNREGISTERED on send
    Stale --> Invalid: 404 UNREGISTERED on send
    Active --> Expired: 270 days inactive\n(Android FCM)
    Stale --> Expired: 270 days inactive\n(Android FCM)
    Invalid --> [*]: Purge from registry
    Expired --> [*]: Purge from registry
